@rob7.bsky.social I put together another Intel NUC bare bones computer running Windows 11 Pro. Plenty of RAM and fast NVMe storage, and a 13th generation processor. Total cost with tax was less than $650.

Windows Update took care of all necessary system files including a BIOS update 😎

